title: Bloomberg Markets: Chart of the Day, Eco Brief for May 30
itunes:title: Bloomberg Markets: Chart of the Day, Eco Brief for May 30
description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Carl J Riccadonna Chief U.S. Economist Bloomberg Intelligence Discussing the economy and markets with Bloomberg Stocks Editor Dave Wilson, who also discusses his Chart of the Day "Tech valuations look nothing like they did in the '90s." Oliver Renick, Bloomberg News Stocks Reporter, also participates in the discussion.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
